image:Adnexed_gills_icon2.svg|Adnexed：蕈褶與蕈柄以一個小接觸點連接
image:Decurrent_gills_icon2.svg|Decurrent：不與菌蓋平行、沿蕈柄向下生長
image:Emarginate_gills_icon2.svg|Emarginate：在抵達蕈柄時突然變短
image:Free_gills_icon2.svg|Free：不與蕈柄相連
image:Seceding gills icon2.svg|Seceding：脫水後脫離蕈柄
image:Sinuate gills icon2.svg|Sinuate：抵達蕈柄前先突然變短，再往蕈柄延伸
image:Subdecurrent gills icon2.svg|Subdecurrent：大致與菌蓋平行，接近蕈柄時向下生長一小段
